<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>All Users</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "style" %>
</head>
<body>
  <div class ="container">
    <div class="cards">
      <div class="detail-top">
        <p>Post 1 by username  <%= @specific_post.author.name %></p>

        <p>Post 1 by username  <%= @specific_user.id %></p>        <p>Comments: <%= @specific_post.comments_counter %> Likes: <%= @specific_post.likes_counter %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="main-section">
      <p>
      <%= @specific_post.text %>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Officiis voluptatum dolores voluptate animi maxime suscipit voluptates placeat vitae aliquam harum assumenda, culpa magnam adipisci incidunt sequi aperiam possimus aliquid doloribus!
